snippet.title: Overwatch 2 Animated Short | “Calling” feat. Sojourn
snippet.description:
With the Overwatch Task Force out of commission, former Captain Sojourn settles into a quiet life of corgis, coffee, and croissants… or so it seems.

An all-new adventure begins with Overwatch 2: Invasion, launching Aug 10!

#Overwatch #Overwatch2 #Gaming
